body_html:
Hi @OleRoel, guys

I was stuck on this problem too, then I rolledback protobuf to version 3.5.1 and it worked for me.

Previously my system had protobuf==3.5.2,post1 and wasn't working then I tried with 3.5.2 and also didn't worked and finally after switch to 3.5.1 it worked.
